  cataloguePssModuleDesignedText: 'Unit can be deployed within 48 hours upon receiving a deployment request; base of operations can be setup within hours once on site, is self-sufficient for 1 month and can operate for up to 4 months.\n\nDesigned for the provision of support to NS initiating or augmenting PSS activities in communities affected by acute crises such as:',
