  catalogueItTelecomTitle: 'ERU IT/Telecom',
  catalogueItTelecomCapacityText: 'The level of support can be scaled to meet operation and context-specific needs. In general, IT&T teams/individuals have knowledge of radio systems (VHF), sat comms (phones, VSAT), power supply, computer desktop support skills and IT network management.',
  catalogueItTelecomEmergencyText: 'The purpose of IT&T Emergency Response Units and delegates is to establish IT and telecommunications networks to help ensure the smooth flow of information within the operation and connect operational actors to external resources.',
