  catalogueLogisticsTitle: 'Logistics ERU',
  catalogueLogisticsCapacityText: 'Logistics ERU organizes logistics in the field and is developed to effectively manage the arrival, clearance, storage and distribution of relief items. The logistics ERU also arranges logistics for arrival of other ERUs.',
  catalogueLogisticsEmergencyText: 'The Logistic ERU can provide the following services:',
