  catalogueReliefDesignedListItem1: 'Programmatic needs and possible modalities for relief support to be delivered (in kind Households items, CBI, emergency shelter material).',
  catalogueReliefDesignedListItem2: 'Operational needs to cover different geographic operational areas or hubs.',
