  catalogueSctSpecifiationNationalSocieties: 'IFRC and NS which have been supporting consistently during the last 5 years but not only limited to them are: Australian RC, British RC, Canadian RC, German RC, Luxemburg RC, Netherland RC, Norwegian RC, Spanish RC, Swedish RC, Swiss RC. Nevertheless, as the SCT is part of the interagency coordination mechanism, there are other organizations and donors outside the Movement that provide support as SDC (Swiss Agency for Development and Cooperation), CRS, ACTED, and IMPACT.',
