  catalogueM15SpecifiationNationalSocieties: 'Austrian, French, German, Spanish',
  catalogueM15VariationText: 'Depending on NS the number of water purification lines (from catchment to delivery to affected people) can vary from 3 to 5.\n\nThis unit could also provide very basic sanitation and hygiene promotion activities to 5,000 people.',
  catalogueMsm20Title: 'MSM20 ERU',
  catalogueMsm20CapacityText: 'Sanitation facilities and hygiene promotion for 20,000 people for a maximum of 4 months according to ERU SOPs.',
  catalogueMsm20EmergencyText: 'Integrated response through:',
  catalogueMsm20EmergencyListItem1: 'Hygiene promotion (including community mobilization, hygiene education, and operation and maintenance).',
  catalogueMsm20EmergencyListItem2: 'Basic sanitation facilities (including latrines, vector control and solid waste disposal) for up to 20,000).',
  catalogueMsm20DesignedText: 'Situations where bad hygiene is consistently practiced by affected people, where there is the danger of diarrhoea, cholera, and other disease outbreaks will persist.',
