  catalogueM40EmergencyListItem1: 'Treatment (with chemical, non filtration) and distribution of up to 600,000 litres of water a day to a population of up to 40,000.',
  catalogueM40EmergencyListItem2: 'The unit can set up nine different storage and distribution points for up to 75,000 litres a day.',
  catalogueM40EmergencyListItem3: 'Distribution and trucking capacity for the transport of treated water to dispersed populations.',
